---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy - LogoPrompt.pro">
  <main class="legal-page">
    <a href="/" class="back-link">&larr; Back to Home</a>

    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="last-updated">Last updated: December 2024</p>

    <section>
      <h2>Introduction</h2>
      <p>
        Welcome to LogoPrompt.pro. We respect your privacy and are committed to protecting any information
        that may be collected while you use our website. This Privacy Policy explains our practices regarding
        data collection and usage.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
      <p>LogoPrompt.pro is designed to be privacy-friendly. We collect minimal information:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Usage Data:</strong> We may collect anonymous usage statistics such as page views,
        browser type, and device information to improve our service.</li>
        <li><strong>Cookies:</strong> We may use essential cookies to ensure the website functions properly.
        These do not track personal information.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>How We Use Information</h2>
      <p>Any information collected is used solely for:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Improving website performance and user experience</li>
        <li>Understanding how visitors interact with our content</li>
        <li>Maintaining website security and preventing abuse</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
      <p>
        Our website displays images from third-party sources (such as Unsplash). When you view these images,
        those services may collect data according to their own privacy policies. We encourage you to review
        the privacy policies of any third-party services you interact with.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Advertising</h2>
      <p>
        We may display advertisements on our website. Third-party advertisers may use cookies and similar
        technologies to serve ads based on your browsing activity. You can opt out of personalized advertising
        through your browser settings or by visiting advertising opt-out pages.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Data Security</h2>
      <p>
        We implement appropriate security measures to protect against unauthorized access, alteration,
        disclosure, or destruction of any data we may collect.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Children's Privacy</h2>
      <p>
        Our website is not directed at children under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personal
        information from children.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
      <p>
        We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page with
        an updated revision date.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Contact Us</h2>
      <p>
        If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us through our website.
      </p>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  .legal-page {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 2rem 1rem 4rem;
  }

  .back-link {
    display: inline-block;
    color: rgb(var(--accent-light));
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    transition: opacity 0.2s;
  }

  .back-link:hover {
    opacity: 0.8;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
    background-image: var(--accent-gradient);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
  }

  .last-updated {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  section {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
    margin: 0 0 0.75rem;
  }

  p {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
  }

  ul {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
    line-height: 1.7;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    margin: 0;
  }

  li {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  strong {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
  }
</style>
